title: Sir Ivan - I Am Peaceman (Hippie music covers)
description:
Sir Ivan's I Am Peaceman album, with tasteful modernized covers of some classic hippie songs

For What It's Worth, Happy Together, Love Is All Around, Imagine, Blowin' In The Wind, San Francisco, Live For Today, Eve Of Destruction, In The Year 2525, Get Together, Here Comes The Sun, Turn Turn Turn

Peace On Earth, Hare Krishna, Kumbaya - original songs of his in that style

320kbps CBR MP3
